[{"id":"1029ecbe7755086eedb58b556a64a5a6","from":"Lesley Groff","from_email":"lesley@nysgllc.com","to":"J. Epstein","to_list":[{"name":"J. Epstein","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"FW: Schedule","date":"2007-11-28T18:55:19.000Z","formatted_date":"Nov 28, 2007","formatted_time":"6:55 PM","body":" \n\n \n\nFrom: kellens@earthlink.net [mailto:kellens@earthlink.net] \nSent: Wednesday, November 28, 2007 1:54 PM\nTo: Lesley Groff\nSubject: Fw: Schedule\n\n \n\n\nHey Les.. can you pass this email on to JE please..thanks.\n\n-----Forwarded Message----- \nFrom: Ana Elisa Aguiar \nSent: Nov 28, 2007 1:46 PM \nTo: kellens@earthlink.net, Thiago Bernardes , Nuno Quintela , bernardo@bja.com.br, Paulo Jacobsen \nSubject: Schedule \n\n\ufeff \n\n \n\n\tSara,\n\n\t \n\n\tWe would like to schedule the presentation of the preliminary studie.\n\n\t \n\n\tWe need the longest time that we can have, so we think that maybe  december 15th will be good. \n\n\tThose are good dates for Jeffrey?\n\n\t \n\n\tFor this metting will be participating Thiago Bernardes, Paulo Jacobsen and the landcape designer Fernando Chacel.\n\n\tWhere this metting can be? In the island or in another place?\n\n\t \n\n\tThanks You,\n\n\t \n\n\tAna Elisa Aguiar\n\tarquiteta \n\n\tBernardes + Jacobsen Arquitetura\n\twww.bernardesjacobsen.com.br\n\n\tRua Corcovado casa 250\n\tJardim Bot\u00e2nico - RJ - BRASIL \n\tCEP 22460-050\n\ttel/fax: 55 11 2512-7743\n\n","body_html":"<html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" xmlns:w=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word\" xmlns:m=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/2004/12/omml\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40\">\n\n<head>\n<meta http-equiv=Content-Type content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\">\n<meta name=Generator content=\"Microsoft Word 12 (filtered medium)\">\n<style>\n<!--\n /* Font Definitions */\n @font-face\n\t{font-family:Calibri;\n\tpanose-1:2 15 5 2 2 2 4 3 2 4;}\n@font-face\n\t{